港爆發「沙士（SARS）」，23條立法亦觸發50萬人上街抗議。由於何志平身為基督徒卻代港人求籤，引來批評，翌年起改由新界鄉議局為香港求籤。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:49:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">主辦的沙田鄉事委員會主席莫錦貴稱是「菩薩意思」，不會更正結果。</span><br />\n咁多人影住，都諗過要造假?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發叔個仔都幾好笑，抽到枝所謂嘅中籤 (其實籤文所寫嘅，都屬於中下)，都可以曲解到去要支持港共施政，佢呢條二世祖真係曲解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eddb19672bd1fe46d31c0e66ac7a78edf8530a3","tid":1010405,"uid":64874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e355afe432d8edec592e15eff7cc3e8f5609ec54","tid":1010405,"uid":195995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84531c26f943bfb1381624f9a0c467f38930eae2","tid":1010405,"uid":64874,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:38:30.000Z","msg":"根本係下籤，只係寫籤班人已經做好預防措施，好似話車公廟上中下比例係442<br />\n除咗東方去黃大仙求籤，其他報紙都無去代表香港求"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:45:06.000Z","msg":"東方支籤點樣？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:50:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/main/20190203/mobile/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fmain%2F20190203%2Fmobile%2Findex.html&d=fwxP8pl6u%2F9ArYBpkrNVTD%2BQayrLlxBj8%2BPX1Ib8Zww%3D&h=fb46e56c\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/main/20190203/mobile/index.html</a><br />\n任你點吹都得"},{"pid":"f36042203a8264b5953cd0c55429e0282cac03e8","tid":1010405,"uid":200328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4eddb19672bd1fe46d31c0e66ac7a78edf8530a3","tid":1010405,"uid":64874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e355afe432d8edec592e15eff7cc3e8f5609ec54","tid":1010405,"uid":195995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84531c26f943bfb1381624f9a0c467f38930eae2","tid":1010405,"uid":64874,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:38:30.000Z","msg":"根本係下籤，只係寫籤班人已經做好預防措施，好似話車公廟上中下比例係442<br />\n除咗東方去黃大仙求籤，其他報紙都無去代表香港求"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:4